{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c1e53945ee","title":"中央转发平原省委关于干部中贪污腐化情况通报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ba99a56caf","index":0,"year":1951,"month":12,"day":15,"articleId":"c1e53945ee"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3e337c9dd0","type":"title","text":"中央转发平原省委关于干部中贪污腐化情况通报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c1e53945ee"},{"id":"74fe00b9af","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c1e53945ee"},{"id":"944a44dd7f","type":"appellation","text":"各中央局，并转分局、省市区党委：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c1e53945ee"},{"id":"6efc9b767e","type":"paragraph","text":"平原省委这一文件集中地暴露了地方干部中存在着严重贪污腐化情况，足以发人深省。望在党内刊物上发表。希望各省市区党委都要发出这样一个文件。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c1e53945ee"},{"id":"b008b7826e","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央十二月十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c1e53945ee"}],"page":{"id":"97ef3e69c8","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c1e53945ee","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"8d63b54c90","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c1e53945ee","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共平原省委1951年12月10日关于反贪污案件的检查、处理及今后发动反贪污斗争给各地市委并报华北局的通报。通报指出，据省纪委上半年统计，违法犯纪受处分的区以上干部中，因贫污、受、蜕化等而受到开除党籍、留党察看、撤销工作等各种党纪处分的占65%。据检察署对14个县的统计，1至8月的违法案件中，贪污读职的占47%。贪污问题绝不是个别的人或个别部门的问题，已是较普遍存在的严重问题。"}],"contents":[{"id":"761cb6cb57","type":"title","text":"中央转发平原省委关于干部中资污腐化情况通报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c1e53945ee"},{"id":"8d63b54c90","type":"paragraph","text":"客中央局，并转分局、省市区党委","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c1e53945ee"},{"id":"a66b8de472","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c1e53945ee"},{"id":"d69345a645","type":"paragraph","text":"平原省委这一文件“集中地暴露了地方干部中存在着严重贪污腐化情况，足以发人深省。望在党内刊物上发表。希望各省市区党委都要发出这样一个文件。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c1e53945ee"},{"id":"d908cf1359","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c1e53945ee"}],"page":{"id":"c8197c80a1","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c1e53945ee","start":146,"end":146}}}},"__N_SSG":true}